('37.72', 'Initial insertion of transvenous leads [electrodes] into atrium and ventricle', 'Excludes: insertion of temporary transvenous pacemaker system (37.78)\n\rreplacement of atrial and/or ventricular lead(s) (37.76)\n', '7', '37', '37.7'),
