('39.53', 'Repair of arteriovenous fistula', 'Embolization of carotid cavernous fistula\n\rRepair of arteriovenous fistula by:\n\r\rclipping\n\r\rcoagulation\n\r\rligation and division\nExcludes: repair of :\n\r\rarteriovenous shunt for renal dialysis (39.42)\n\r\rhead and neck vessels, endovascular approach (39.72) \n\r\rthat with:\n\r\r\rgraft replacement (38.40-38.49)\n\r\r\rresection (38.30-38.49, 38.60-38.69)\n', '7', '39', '39.5'),
