('00.70', 'Revision of hip replacement, both acetabular and femoral components', 'Total hip revision\n\rCode also any:\n\r\rremoval of (cement) (joint) spacer (84.57)\n\r\rtype of bearing surface, if known (00.74-00.77)\nExcludes:\n\r\rrevision of hip replacement, acetabular component only (00.71)\n\r\rrevision of hip replacement, femoral component only (00.72)\n\r\rrevision of hip replacement, Not Otherwise Specified (81.53)\n\r\rrevision with replacement of acetabular liner and/or femoral head only (00.73)\n', '0', '00'),
