lacement device(s) (84.85)\n\rrevision of interspinous process device(s) (84.81)\n\r84.84Insertion or replacement of facet replacement device(s)\n\rFacet arthroplasty\nExcludes: initial insertion of pedicle screws with spinal fusion- omit code\n\rinsertion or replacement of interspinous process device(s) (84.80)\n\rinsertion or replacement of pedicle-based dynamic stabilization device(s) (84.82)\n\rreplacement of pedicle screws used in spinal fusion (78.59)\n\r84.85Revision of facet replacement device(s)\n\rRepair of previously inserted facet replacement device(s)\nExcludes: removal of pedicle screws used in spinal fusion (78.69)\n\rreplacement of pedicle screws used in spinal fusion (78.59)\n\rrevision of interspinous process device(s) (84.81)\n\rrevision of pedicle-based dynamic stabilization device(s) (84.83)\n', '14', '84'),
